  <title> Continuity</title>

  <paragraphs>
    <title>Module Learning Objectives</title>
  
    <ol>
      <li>Define what it means for a function to be <u>continuous</u> and classify different types of <u>discontinuities</u>.</li>
      <li> Decide where a piecewise defined function is continuous.</li>
      <li>State the <u>Intermediate Value Theorem</u> and describe the intuition behind.</li>
    </ol>
  </paragraphs>

 

