  <paragraphs>
    <title>Post-video reflection</title>
    <p> Suppose the definition of the piecewise defined function changes at a values <m>x=a</m>. Is <m>a</m> the <em>only</em> spot you need to check for continuity, or do you need to still check the rest?
    </p>
  </paragraphs>



